        <Parent_String>collective settlements [300008523], settlements by ownership [300008522], inhabited places [300008347], Settlements and Landscapes (hierarchy name) [300008346], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
